Normally it is cooked in an outdoor oven but it works just as well on the stove top. [/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css=".vc_custom_1444912400691{padding-top: 20px !important;}"][vc_column_inner width="1/6" offset="vc_hidden-xs"][vc_single_image image="84" img_size="100x100" alignment="center" style="vc_box_circle_2" css_animation="left-to-right"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="5/6" css=".vc_custom_1444912021066{padding-top: 20px !important;}"][vc_column_text css_animation="right-to-left"]Manti a famous meal from my country. To prepare this dish takes time, but I'm sure you'll agree it's worth it! Enjoy—afiyet olsun (bon appetit)![/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css=".vc_custom_1444912400691{padding-top: 20px !important;}"][vc_column_inner width="1/6" offset="vc_hidden-xs"][vc_single_image image="85" img_size="100x100" alignment="center" style="vc_box_circle_2" css_animation="left-to-right"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="5/6" css=".vc_custom_1444912021066{padding-top: 20px !important;}"][vc_column_text css_animation="right-to-left"]Iskender Kebab I was amazed by its delicious taste! I later found out that this dish was named after Alexander the Great, whom the Persians called 'Iskender.' Apparently it was his favourite food.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_column_text css_animation="bottom-to-top" css=".vc_custom_1446042713048{padding-top: 50px !important;}"]

Soups & Barbecue

Best of all, kids can get in on the fun and help parents cook. [/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]
